uages\"><b><a href=\"/wiki/Bec_de_corbin\" title=\"Bec de corbin\">English</a></b>\n<p><span></span>\n<span></span>\n<span></span>\n<span></span>\n</p>\n&#160;&#8226;&#32;<span lang=\"zh-CN\"><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">中文（中国大陆）‎</a></span></div>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\">\n<table class=\"prettytable\" style=\"margin: 0;\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><span class=\"nhsym clr-cyan\">)</span> <a href=\"/wiki/File:Bec_de_corbin.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Bec de corbin.png\" src=\"/images/c/cb/Bec_de_corbin.png\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /></a>\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>名称\n</th>\n<td>鸦啄战锤\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>外观\n</th>\n<td>喙状长柄武器\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>伤害（小型）\n</th>\n<td>d8\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>伤害（大型）\n</th>\n<td>d6\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>命中修正\n</th>\n<td>+0\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>武器技能类别\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/%E9%95%BF%E6%9F%84%E6%AD%A6%E5%99%A8\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"长柄武器\">长柄武器</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>规格\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/index.php?title=%E5%8F%8C%E6%89%8B&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"双手 (page does not exist)\">双手</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>基础价\n</th>\n<td>8 <a href=\"/wiki/Zm/zh-CN\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Zm/zh-CN\">zm</a><br />（+10/正数附魔等级）\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>重量\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/index.php?title=%E9%87%8D%E9%87%8F&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"重量 (page does not exist)\">100</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>材料\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/index.php?title=%E9%93%81&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"铁 (page does not exist)\">铁</a>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n</div>\n<dl><dd><i>“喙长柄武器”重定向至此。</i></dd></dl>\n<p><b>鸦啄战锤</b>（bec de corbin）是<a href=\"/index.php?title=NetHack/zh-CN&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"NetHack/zh-CN (page does not exist)\">NetHack</a>中的一种<a href=\"/wiki/%E6%AD%A6%E5%99%A8\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"武器\">武器</a>。它是一种<a href=\"/wiki/%E9%95%BF%E6%9F%84%E6%AD%A6%E5%99%A8\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"长柄武器\">长柄武器</a>，由<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E9%93%81&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"铁 (page does not exist)\">铁</a>制成，未<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E9%89%B4%E5%AE%9A&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"鉴定 (page does not exist)\">鉴定</a>时外观为<b>喙状长柄武器</b>（beaked polearm）。\n</p>\n<div class=\"upcoming\">\n<p><i>以下内容涉及即将到来的版本（<a href=\"/wiki/3.7.0\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"3.7.0\">3.7.0</a>）之信息。如果该版本已发布，请验证此处信息是否准确，并作出相应修改，以将其并入页面。</i>\n</p>\n根据<a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/NetHack/NetHack/commit/1ae2bc7063ebe3c3831a707efd3fc3d6fd638d26\">commit 1ae2bc70</a>，现在若<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E7%8E%A9%E5%AE%B6&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"玩家 (page does not exist)\">玩家</a>持握鸦啄战锤，所有<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E4%B9%8C%E9%B8%A6&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"乌鸦 (page does not exist)\">乌鸦</a>均会以和平状态生成。</div>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\" /><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#.E7.94.9F.E6.88.90\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">生成</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#.E7.AD.96.E7.95.A5\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">策略</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#.E5.8E.86.E5.8F.B2\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">历史</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#.E8.B5.B7.E6.BA.90\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">起源</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Variants\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Variants</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#dNetHack\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">dNetHack</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#NetHack_Fourk\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">NetHack Fourk</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#xNetHack\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">xNetHack</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#EvilHack\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">EvilHack</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-10\"><a href=\"#.E7.99.BE.E7.A7.91.E6.96.87.E6.9C.AC\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">百科文本</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-11\"><a href=\"#.E5.BC.95.E7.94.A8.E5.8F.8A.E6.B3.A8.E9.87.8A\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">7</span> <span class=\"toctext\">引用及注释</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span id=\"生成\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E7.94.9F.E6.88.90\">生成</span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php?title=%E8%AD%A6%E5%8D%AB%E5%91%98&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"警卫员 (page does not exist)\">警卫员</a>和<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E5%A3%AB%E5%85%B5&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"士兵 (page does not exist)\">士兵</a>在生成时有可能<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E6%80%AA%E7%89%A9%E8%B5%B7%E5%A7%8B%E7%89%A9%E5%93%81&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"怪物起始物品 (page does not exist)\">携带</a>鸦啄战锤<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>。\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"策略\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E7.AD.96.E7.95.A5\">策略</span></h2>\n<p>与其他长柄武器相比，鸦啄战锤对小型怪物的伤害不错，但对大型怪物的平均伤害与<a href=\"/wiki/%E7%90%89%E6%A3%AE%E9%94%A4\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"琉森锤\">琉森锤</a>同为最低，而且<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E9%87%8D%E9%87%8F&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"重量 (page does not exist)\">重量</a>也不低。\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"历史\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E5.8E.86.E5.8F.B2\">历史</span></h2>\n<p>鸦啄战锤最初于<a href=\"/wiki/NetHack_1.3d\" title=\"NetHack 1.3d\">NetHack 1.3d</a>加入游戏。\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"起源\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E8.B5.B7.E6.BA.90\">起源</span></h2>\n<div class=\"noprint sidebox\">\n<div style=\"float: left;\"><div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:Fair-use-wikipedia-logo.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"维基百科\"><img alt=\"维基百科\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f8/Fair-use-wikipedia-logo.png/50px-Fair-use-wikipedia-logo.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/f/f8/Fair-use-wikipedia-logo.png 1.5x\" /></a></div></div>\n<div style=\"margin-left: 60px;\"><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/zh:Main_Page\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"wikipedia:zh:Main Page\">维基百科</a>相关条目：\n<div style=\"margin-left: 10px;\"><i><b><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bec_de_corbin\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"wikipedia:Bec de corbin\">Bec de corbin</a></b></i></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:210px;\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:Becdecorbins.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/0/05/Becdecorbins.png\" width=\"208\" height=\"103\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:Becdecorbins.png\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>鸦啄战锤</div></div></div>\n<p>鸦啄战锤（bec de corbin，古法语“鸦喙”的意思，复数形式为“becs de corbin”）是在中世纪晚期的欧洲被广泛使用的一种长柄武器。鸦啄战锤的攻击部由一个改造过的锤头，一个尖头和一个粗壮的喙状端组成，固定在长柄的一端。锤头一般是钝的（也有带分叉的锤头），通常作为配重而非攻击手段，主要作用是协助喙状端击破板甲之类的护甲。鸦啄战锤的尖头比起<a href=\"/wiki/%E7%90%89%E6%A3%AE%E9%94%A4\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"琉森锤\">琉森锤</a>来说一般要短粗一些。“bec de corbin”这个词有时也用来描述一些其他种类的<a href=\"/wiki/%E6%88%98%E9%94%A4\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"战锤\">战锤</a>，例如大槌（maul）或骑兵战镐（horseman's pick）。\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Variants\">Variants</span></h2>\n<div class=\"todo\">\n<p><b>此条目或段落的部分内容需要翻译。</b><br />\n您可以帮助我们<a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://nethackwiki.com/index.php?title=Bec_de_corbin/zh-CN&amp;action=edit\"><b>翻译此页面</b></a>，但<b>请勿使用机器翻译</b>。\n</p>\n</div>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"dNetHack\">dNetHack</span></h3>\n<p>In <a href=\"/wiki/DNetHack\" title=\"DNetHack\">dNetHack</a> and <a href=\"/wiki/NotdNetHack\" title=\"NotdNetHack\">notdNetHack</a>, the bec de corbin has its weight reduced to 75 aum.\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"NetHack_Fourk\">NetHack Fourk</span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"/wiki/NetHack_Fourk\" title=\"NetHack Fourk\">NetHack Fourk</a> removes the bec de corbin and many other polearms.\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"xNetHack\">xNetHack</span></h3>\n<p>In <a href=\"/wiki/XNetHack\" title=\"XNetHack\">xNetHack</a>, the bec de corbin is one of the few polearms that is not removed. It is also buffed to deal the same damage as the removed lucern hammer.\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"EvilHack\">EvilHack</span></h3>\n<p>In <a href=\"/wiki/EvilHack\" title=\"EvilHack\">EvilHack</a>, a bec de corbin can be created at a <a href=\"/wiki/Forge_(dungeon_feature)\" title=\"Forge (dungeon feature)\">forge</a> by combining a <a href=\"/wiki/War_hammer\" title=\"War hammer\">war hammer</a> and a <a href=\"/wiki/Spear\" title=\"Spear\">spear</a>. This also applies to <a href=\"/wiki/Hack%27EM\" title=\"Hack&#39;EM\">Hack'EM</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"百科文本\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E7.99.BE.E7.A7.91.E6.96.87.E6.9C.AC\">百科文本</span></h2>\n<dl><dd><i>请参阅<a href=\"/wiki/%E9%95%BF%E6%9F%84%E6%AD%A6%E5%99%A8#.E7.99.BE.E7.A7.91.E6.96.87.E6.9C.AC\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"长柄武器\">长柄武器的百科文本</a>。</i></dd></dl>\n<h2><span id=\"引用及注释\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E5.BC.95.E7.94.A8.E5.8F.8A.E6.B3.A8.E9.87.8A\">引用及注释</span></h2>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/NetHack/NetHack/blob/NetHack-3.6.7_Released/src/makemon.c#L194\">src/makemon.c in NetHack 3.6.7, line 194</a>\n     </span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<div style=\"display:none; right:10px; padding-bottom: 17px\" class=\"metadata topicon nopopups\"><div style=\"margin-top: -10px\"><a href=\"/wiki/NetHackWiki:Next_version\" title=\"此条目的内容已同步至NetHack 3.6.7。详细信息请点击此处。\"><img alt=\"此条目的内容已同步至NetHack 3.6.7。详细信息请点击此处。\" src=\"/images/f/f7/Nh367-icon.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20240926182531\nCache expiry: 604800\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.038 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.053 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 434/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 2652/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 5186/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 989/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 9/40\nExpensive parser function count: 4/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 448/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   32.935      1 -total\n 18.88%    6.219      1 Template:Languages\n 13.91%    4.582      1 Template:Nethack-367/zh-CN\n 13.75%    4.530      1 Template:Refsrc\n 13.33%    4.391      5 Template:Languages/Lang\n 12.40%    4.085      1 Template:Weapon/zh-CN\n 10.38%    3.419      1 Template:Version_icon/zh-CN\n  7.68%    2.528      1 Template:Upcoming/zh-CN\n  7.27%    2.395      1 Template:Wikipedia/zh-CN\n  6.87%    2.264      1 Template:Redirects-here/zh-CN\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key wikihackdb:pcache:idhash:39540-0!canonical and timestamp 20240926182531 and revision id 166817\n -->\n</div></div>\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"printfooter\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\tRetrieved from \"<a dir=\"ltr\" href=\"https://nethackwiki.com/index.php?title=Bec_de_corbin/zh-CN&amp;oldid=166817\">https://nethackwiki.com/index.php?title=Bec_de_corbin/zh-CN&amp;oldid=166817<